            "type": "text",
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 2 of SLEEP: A 30-Day Tapping Intensive. The script targets the physical holding pattern that sleep difficulty creates: the jaw that stays clenched, the shoulders that don't come down, the chest that remains tight through the day. Use it during daylight hours, when the tension has accumulated and needs to be released before it follows you to bed."
          }
        ]
      },
